			<div class="content" id="post-content-2489164">
									

<blockquote>
<p>SCP-663 is to be kept in the second floor break room at Site 19.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>this was written back in 2009, when &quot;let's have the Foundation use this anomalous thing with no concern about what side effects it might have&quot; was the mindset.</p>
<p>This is a water purifier which tortures humans to death as an essential component of the process of generating drinkable water, and which cannot be shut off. I can see how there's a certain symbolism to it, but it does not make sense for the Foundation to keep this item in the break room for everyone to use as a source of drinking water.</p>

							</div>

								
					
